@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Register Applicant

start
:Applicant fills signup form;
:Frontend sends POST /api/auth/register-applicant;
:Server finds user by email in database;
if (User exists?) then (yes)
  :Return 400 "User already exists";
  stop
else (no)
  :Hash password using bcrypt;
  :Create user account with role=applicant;
  :Create applicant profile in database;
  :Sign JWT token;
  if (Send welcome email enabled?) then (yes)
    :Send welcome email via SMTP (Brevo);
  endif
  :Return 200 with token, user data, and applicant profile;
  :Frontend displays success;
endif
stop

@enduml
